<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no" />
        <meta name="description" content="Trang tin điện tử nhiều người xem nhất vũ trụ." />
        <meta name="author" content="Huỳnh Thành Đạt" />
        <title><%= (typeof baiviet !== "undefined") ? baiviet.TieuDe : 'N/A' %> - Trang tin điện tử</title>
        <link href="http://127.0.0.1:3000/css/app.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    </head>
    <body>
        <%- include('header') %>
        <main class="main pt-4">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-9">
                        <% if(typeof baiviet !== "undefined") { %>
                        <article class="card mb-4">
                            <header class="card-header text-center">
                                <div class="card-meta">
                                    <a href="#"><time class="timeago" datetime="<%= baiviet.NgayDang %>"></time></a>
                                    thuộc
                                    <a href="/baiviet/chude/<%= baiviet.ChuDe._id %>"><%= baiviet.ChuDe.TenChuDe %></a>
                                </div>
                                <a href="post-image.html">
                                    <h3 class="card-title"><%= baiviet.TieuDe %></h3>
                                </a>
                            </header>
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p style="text-align: justify"><strong><%= baiviet.TomTat %></strong></p>
                                <%- baiviet.NoiDung %>

                                <hr />
                                <h3>2 bình luận</h3>
                                <div class="d-flex mb-3 p-3 bg-light">
                                    <div class="text-center">
                                        <img
                                            class="me-3 rounded-circle"
                                            src="http://127.0.0.1:3000/images/avatars/1.png"
                                            width="100"
                                            height="100"
                                        />
                                        <h6 class="mt-1 mb-0 me-3">Kim</h6>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex-grow-1">
                                        <p class="mt-3 mb-2">
                                            Vestibulum volutpat pretium libero. Cras id dui. Aenean ut eros et nisl
                                            sagittis vestibulum. Nullam nulla eros, ultricies sit amet, nonummy id,
                                            imperdiet feugiat, pede. Sed lectus. Donec mollis hendrerit risus. Phasellus
                                            nec sem thuộc justo pellentesque facilisis.
                                        </p>
                                        <time class="timeago text-muted" datetime="2021-09-20 20:00"
                                            >20 november 2021</time
                                        >
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="d-flex mb-3 p-3 bg-light">
                                    <div class="text-center">
                                        <img
                                            class="me-3 rounded-circle"
                                            src="http://127.0.0.1:3000/images/avatars/2.png"
                                            width="100"
                                            height="100"
                                        />
                                        <h6 class="mt-1 mb-0 me-3">Paula</h6>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex-grow-1">
                                        <p class="mt-3 mb-2">
                                            Nam pretium turpis et arcu. Duis arcu tortor, suscipit eget, imperdiet nec,
                                            imperdiet iaculis, ipsum. Sed aliquam ultrices mauris. Integer ante arcu,
                                            accumsan a, consectetuer eget, posuere ut, mauris. Praesent adipiscing.
                                            Phasellus ullamcorper ipsum rutrum nunc. Nunc nonummy metus.
                                        </p>
                                        <time class="timeago text-muted" datetime="2021-09-05 20:00"
                                            >5 november 2021</time
                                        >
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mt-5">
                                    <h5>Write a response</h5>
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-md-6">
                                            <input
                                                type="text"
                                                class="form-control"
                                                id="name"
                                                name="name"
                                                placeholder="Your name"
                                            />
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-md-6">
                                            <input
                                                type="email"
                                                class="form-control"
                                                id="email"
                                                name="email"
                                                placeholder="Your email"
                                            />
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <textarea
                                        class="form-control mt-3"
                                        rows="3"
                                        placeholder="Write a response.."
                                    ></textarea>
                                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-success mt-3">Publish</a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </article>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3 ms-auto">
                        <aside class="sidebar">
                            <div class="card mb-4">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h4 class="card-title">Giới thiệu</h4>
                                    <p class="card-text">
                                        Đọc tin tức trên trang web này sẽ giúp bạn có cái nhìn khách quan về cuộc sống.
                                        Đừng quên chia sẻ trang này cho toàn bộ vũ trụ biết nhé. Mến yêu.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </aside>
                        <aside class="sidebar sidebar-sticky">
                            <div class="card mb-4">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h4 class="card-title">Thẻ</h4>
                                    <% if(typeof chuyenmuc !== "undefined") { chuyenmuc.forEach(cd => { %>
                                    <a class="btn btn-light btn-sm mb-1" href="/baiviet/chude/<%= cd._id %>"
                                        ><%= cd.TenChuDe %></a
                                    >
                                    <% }); } %>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="card mb-4">
                                <div class="card-body">
                                    <h4 class="card-title">Xem nhiều nhất</h4>
                                    <% if(typeof xemnhieunhat !== "undefined") { xemnhieunhat.forEach(bv => { %>
                                    <a href="/baiviet/chitiet/<%= bv._id %>" class="d-inline-block mt-3">
                                        <h4 class="h6"><%= bv.TieuDe %></h4>
                                        <img class="card-img" src="<%- firstImage(bv.NoiDung) %>" alt="" />
                                    </a>
                                    <time class="timeago" datetime="<%= bv.NgayDang %>"></time> thuộc <%=
                                    bv.ChuDe.TenChuDe %> <% }); } %>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </aside>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
        <%- include('footer-2') %> <%- include('javascript') %>
    </body>
</html>
